2013年6月，他说，整个英国过早死亡率高的区域的变化令人震惊。数据显示，[[利物浦|利物浦]]和[[曼彻斯特|曼彻斯特]]是英国过早死亡率最高的地方之一。

2013年6月，他还宣布计划允许外国国民在缴费的情况下使用国民卫生服务，但声称这会使国民卫生服务的成本增加2亿英镑，但官方数字为3300万英镑。<ref name="Rowena">{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/health/10151282/Crackdown-on-NHS-health-tourists.html|title=Crackdown on NHS 'health tourists'|first=Rowena|last=Mason|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=30 June 2013|accessdate=2 July 2013|location=London|archive-date=2013-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703100442/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/health/10151282/Crackdown-on-NHS-health-tourists.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>后来3300万英镑中的2100万成本被收回，所以实际成本在1200万磅，小于亨特强制关闭的最高成本上限。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/politics/2013/07/why-hunts-crackdown-health-tourism-could-cost-more-it-saves|title=Why Hunt's crackdown on "health tourism" could cost more than it saves|work=[[New_Statesman|New Statesman]]|date=3 July 2013|last=Eaton|first=George|accessdate=2019-07-04|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129081259/https://www.newstatesman.com/politics/2013/07/why-hunts-crackdown-health-tourism-could-cost-more-it-saves|dead-url=no}}</ref>

据报道，2013年12月，亨特因[[急诊室|急诊室]]错过病患一事亲自打电话给国家卫生服务{{le|医院信托|Hospital trust}}的主席，{{le|护理质量委员会|Care Quality Commission}}主席David Prior描述此舉为“疯狂”。此前，一位[[英国保守党|保守党]]议员说亨特像他的[[英国工党|工党]]前辈一样勤于履职，结果却是本应拨付给初级和社区护理的资金被拨给了急诊。<ref>{{cite news|title=Jeremy Hunt crazy to call hospital bosses, says regulator|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-25476090|accessdate=21 December 2013|publisher=BBC News|date=21 December 2013|archive-date=2019-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417070150/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-25476090|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一方面，{{le|皇家紧急医学学院|Royal College of Emergency Medicine}}院长Clifford Mann博士指责2012年《{{le|卫生与社会关怀法|Health and Social Care Act 2012}}》中的问题导致了“[[决策|决策]]瘫痪”，使全英国缺乏约375名急诊医生。<ref name="charlie">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/exclusive-it-was-no-accident--government-blamed-for-ae-crisis-9032119.html|title=Exclusive: 'It was no accident' – Government blamed for A&E crisis|first=Charlie|last=Cooper|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=31 December 2013|accessdate=1 January 2014|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925170204/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/exclusive-it-was-no-accident--government-blamed-for-ae-crisis-9032119.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年3月，亨特宣布，政府不会向国民卫生服务的非医疗人员提供推荐的1％的薪酬增长（约占员工总数的55％）。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2014/mar/13/unions-threaten-strike-action-nhs-pay-settlement-unite-gmb|title=Unions threaten strike action over NHS pay settlement|accessdate=18 March 2014|work=The Guardian|date=13 March 2014|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119064454/https://www.theguardian.com/society/2014/mar/13/unions-threaten-strike-action-nhs-pay-settlement-unite-gmb|dead-url=no}}</ref>那年年末，他宣称患者的选择并不是改善NHS表现的关键，这与保守党和工党政府过去12年的政策偏好相比有很大突破。他表示“医疗保健中存在自然垄断，而患者的选择永远不会推动变化。”<ref>{{cite news|title=Patient choice is not key to improving performance, says Hunt|url=http://www.hsj.co.uk/news/acute-care/exclusive-patient-choice-is-not-key-to-improving-performance-says-hunt/5077051.article|accessdate=14 December 2014|work=Health Service Journal|date=26 November 2014|last=West|first=Dave|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810185922/https://www.hsj.co.uk/news/acute-care/exclusive-patient-choice-is-not-key-to-improving-performance-says-hunt/5077051.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年4月[[2015年英国大选|大选]]前，医院院长们被曝瓜分了3500万英镑涨薪的6%，亨特说如果保守党赢得大选就调查此事。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.itv.com/news/2015-04-20/nhs-chiefs-handed-35-million-in-pay-rises/|title=NHS chiefs 'handed £35 million in pay rises'|publisher=ITV News|date=20 April 2015|accessdate=27 December 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115710/https://www.itv.com/news/2015-04-20/nhs-chiefs-handed-35-million-in-pay-rises|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2014年11月的《健康服务杂志》采访中，他说他想作为卫生大臣工作到2017年。2015年7月亨特的一张宣传海报的背景中出现了一位患者的个人信息，他被批评破坏了保密原则。

2015年7月，亨特成为新英国政府网站上第一次请愿的主角，达到了要求在国会辩论的请愿书所需的10万个签名的门槛。由{{le|会诊医生|Consultant (medicine)}}发起的请愿活动要求对卫生大臣亨特进行不信任投票。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Petition calling for health secretary’s resignation exceeds 200 000 supporters|url=https://www.bmj.com/content/351/bmj.h4101|last=Rimmer|first=Abi|date=28 July 2015|journal=BMJ|accessdate=5 June 2019|doi=10.1136/bmj.h4101|volume=351|pages=h4101|pmid=26220673|via=www.bmj.com|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626183002/https://www.bmj.com/content/351/bmj.h4101|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/mps-debate-jeremy-hunt-sacking-6117332|title=MPs will debate Jeremy Hunt sacking petition – but Tories could block it at first hurdle|website=Daily Mirror|date=22 July 2015|accessdate=28 July 2015|first=Dan|last=Bloom|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120161151/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/mps-debate-jeremy-hunt-sacking-6117332|dead-url=no}}</ref>请愿书最终获得了222,991个签名，导致2015年9月14日国会就该问题举行辩论。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Mikey|title=Andy Burnham promises to table vote of no confidence in Jeremy Hunt after 200,000 sign petition|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/andy-burnham-promises-table-vote-6148268|website=Daily Mirror|accessdate=28 July 2015|date=27 July 2015|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128191759/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/andy-burnham-promises-table-vote-6148268|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，请愿委员会没有权力进行不信任投票，<ref>{{cite web|title=How Tories can block this petition to sack Jeremy Hunt at the first hurdle|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/mps-debate-jeremy-hunt-sacking-6117332|accessdate=5 June 2019|date=22 July 2015|last=Bloom|first=Dan|website=mirror|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120161151/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/mps-debate-jeremy-hunt-sacking-6117332|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Parliament shuns debate on Jeremy Hunt's removal as health secretary|url=http://www.pulsetoday.co.uk/news/political-news/parliament-shuns-debate-on-jeremy-hunts-removal-as-health-secretary/20020055.article|accessdate=5 June 2019|last=Lind|first=Sofia|website=Pulse Today|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626182952/http://www.pulsetoday.co.uk/news/political-news/parliament-shuns-debate-on-jeremy-hunts-removal-as-health-secretary/20020055.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>辩论也不是由全下院进行，一个下院委员会对去过卫生服务工作人员的合同和条件进行了辩论。<ref>{{cite web|title=NHS (Contracts and Conditions)|url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201516/cmhansrd/cm150914/halltext/150914h0001.htm#15091415000001|accessdate=16 September 2015|publisher=Parliament of the United Kingdom|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808180752/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201516/cmhansrd/cm150914/halltext/150914h0001.htm#15091415000001|dead-url=no}}</ref>政府对请愿网站的答复也没有解决医生们对亨特的信心问题。
