2015年《每日电讯报》的卧底调查显示，由业务流程外包和专业服务公司Capita所有的一些代理机构、医疗保险和私人护理机构向一些医院收取较高的费用，并给予虚假的公司详细资料。这些机构收取高达49％的费用。亨特批评那些寻求“高利润”的公司牺牲了国民卫生服务和纳税人的利益，并承诺“减少产生新的利润敲诈机构”。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/nhs/12064455/NHS-hit-by-nurses-pay-scandal.html|title=NHS hit by locum agency nurses' pay scandal|work=The Daily Telegraph|first1=Lyndsey T|last1=elford|first2=Claire|last2=Newell|first3=Edward|last3=Malnick|first4=Luke|last4=Heighton|date=22 December 2015|accessdate=25 December 2015|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224024510/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/nhs/12064455/NHS-hit-by-nurses-pay-scandal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年1月30日亨特建议父母如果担心自己孩子可能有脑膜炎，应该先上网看看皮疹的照片以防误判的报告再次被医疗专业人士谴责。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/jeremy-hunt-the-two-most-horrifying-moments-of-my-career-as-a-doctor-started-with-a-child-and-a-rash-a6847011.html|title=Jeremy Hunt, the two most horrifying moments of my career as a doctor started with a child and a rash|first=Amrita|last=Jesurasa|date=1 February 2016|work=The Independent|accessdate=2019-07-04|archive-date=2019-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429044723/https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/jeremy-hunt-the-two-most-horrifying-moments-of-my-career-as-a-doctor-started-with-a-child-and-a-rash-a6847011.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>亨特的言论被引述为“如果你担心你的孩子患了皮疹，治疗的第一步是上网看图片并说：‘我的孩子的皮疹看起来像这一个’-这可能是自行诊断的好办法。”亨特的言论被广泛批评是由于致命的脑膜炎引起的皮疹看起来非常类似于其他情况，以及脑膜炎的发病时间。许多医生采用社交媒体来强调这些危险，他们的专业意见是，从公共卫生的角度来看，亨特的评论是潜在的危险。脑膜炎慈善机构说亨特的建议是“可能致命的”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Don't Google a rash|url=https://www.meningitisnow.org/support-us/news-centre/news-stories/dont-google-rash/|date=1 February 2016|publisher=[[Meningitis_Trust|Meningitis Trust]]|access-date=2019-07-04|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626183003/https://www.meningitisnow.org/support-us/news-centre/news-stories/dont-google-rash/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

