f>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/jeremy-hunt-brexit-replace-foreign-doctors-british-nhs-eu-a7341256.html|title=Jeremy Hunt: We can replace foreign doctors with British talent after Brexit|work=The Independent|date=2 October 2016|accessdate=2 October 2016|last=Agerholm|first=Harriet|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108174715/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/jeremy-hunt-brexit-replace-foreign-doctors-british-nhs-eu-a7341256.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在当月晚些时候的保守党年会上，亨特承诺到2025年，国民卫生服务将实现“医生自给自足”。他宣布在2018年在英国医学院校增加多达1500个额外的名额，其中一部分资金来自国际医学学生费用的增加。亨特还表示，英国医学生将被迫在国民卫生服务工作至少四年，或者偿还他们大约22万英镑的培训费用。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/oct/03/jeremy-hunt-promises-to-end-nhs-reliance-on-overseas-doctors-after-brexit|title=Hunt promises to end NHS reliance on overseas doctors after Britain leaves EU|work=The Guardian|date=4 October 2016|last1=Stewart|first1=Heather|last2=Campbell|first2=Denis|accessdate=2019-07-04|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095111/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/oct/03/jeremy-hunt-promises-to-end-nhs-reliance-on-overseas-doctors-after-brexit|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-37546360|title=Student doctor numbers to rise by 25%|publisher=BBC News|date=4 October 2016|last=Triggle|first=Nick|accessdate=2019-07-04|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119061140/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-37546360|dead-url=no}}</ref>

